<span class="doc-tag">.q2w-header</span>
<h1 class="doc-h1">Header</h1>
<p class="doc-lead">Floating brand bar with logo, title, optional subtitle, and right-aligned action buttons. q2w-mapcss ships multiple real header styles for dashboards, technical maps, and public-facing qgis2web exports.</p>

